Air Berlin Hedged 84 Percent of Second-Quarter Jet Fuel Needs

-- B y   R a c h e l   G r a h a m
-- 
2011-03-24T12:39:41Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-24/air-berlin-hedged-84-percent-of-second-quarter-jet-fuel-needs.html
Air Berlin Plc (AB1) ,  Germany ’s second-
biggest airline, said it hedged 84 percent of its jet-fuel
requirements for the second quarter of this year.  The airline hedged 76 percent for the third quarter and 22
percent in the subsequent three-month period, according to a
 presentation  posted on the company’s website.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Rachel Graham in London 
